main event: An approximately one-yard long torpedo-shaped object was observed flying slowly from east to west over Frederikshaab, Greenland, on January 14, 1959.
interesting points: The object was observed for 4 minutes, The sighting was made by several persons, The object was initially thought to be an aircraft, There were reports of similar sightings in the vicinity on the same date, The object may have been a balloon or an astronomical phenomenon according to various conclusions.
